description:
What does Psalm 77 tell us about God's plan of salvation? How does understanding the Old Testament sanctuary and sacrificial offering prove that God had a plan to save humanity from the very beginning? 

God knew that sin would enter the universe, but as Psalm 77 tells us, He had a plan in place to ensure His people would be saved. In the Biblical record of the Old Testament sanctuary and stories of the sacrificial offering, God's consistency of character is once again demonstrated. 

Take an in-depth look at the sanctuary and how understanding it is vital to understanding the plan of salvation. See proof of God's trustworthiness. Discover the amazing love of Christ the Redeemer for you.
